02:53.300 --> 02:54.470
Well, I have a theory.

02:54.670 --> 02:56.370
If it was definitely
someone on the bus.

02:56.570 --> 02:57.540
Well, it wasn't me.

02:57.740 --> 02:58.770
- No one's talking
about you, Tia.

02:58.970 --> 03:00.580
Literally no one ever talks
about you.

03:00.780 --> 03:02.350
Who's your suspect?

03:02.540 --> 03:04.950
Blake Navarro.

03:05.150 --> 03:07.250
Remember what she was like
last year, you guys?

03:07.450 --> 03:08.720
Like, completely normal.

03:08.920 --> 03:10.390
And then her parents
get divorced

03:10.590 --> 03:12.490
