06:51.140 --> 06:52.240
He's got something.

06:52.440 --> 06:54.540
- What if they're still trying
to kill us?

06:54.740 --> 06:55.710
What if they killed Connor?

06:55.910 --> 06:57.310
- He was bitten too.
- Who's Connor?

06:57.510 --> 07:00.220
- [cage rattles loudly]
- Whispering is talking.

07:00.420 --> 07:02.890
