what doesn't look good

09:25.730 --> 09:27.130
on a college application, Tia?
An criminal record.

09:27.330 --> 09:28.330
It wasn't my idea.

09:28.530 --> 09:30.100
I didn't even know
we were going.

09:30.300 --> 09:32.070
- You do not have
a check-in yet.

