09:41.780 --> 09:43.810
Is there a hospital
I should bring her to?

09:44.010 --> 09:44.950
[overlapping urgent chatter]

09:45.150 --> 09:47.050
Follow me.

09:47.250 --> 09:48.650
<i>* *</i>

09:48.850 --> 09:50.520
Miller.

09:50.720 --> 09:57.830
<i>* *</i>

09:58.260 --> 10:00.260
- I can't believe you
left our fucking dog.

10:00.460 --> 10:02.630
I need a new prescription.

10:02.830 --> 10:04.100
No, I didn't finish it.

10:04.300 --> 10:06.340
It went up in flames like
the rest of my goddamn house.

10:06.530 --> 10:09.400
- I said five beds.
Two adults, three kids.

10:09.600 --> 10:10.840
We need five.

10:11.040 --> 10:13.810
[overlapping chatter]

10:14.010 --> 10:15.180
<i>* *</i>

10:15.380 --> 10:16.410
- No. The others are still
answering questions.

10:16.610 --> 10:18.210
Because the cops said
four teenagers

10:18.410 --> 10:19.820
were seen at the origin
of the fire.

10:20.020 --> 10:22.920
[heartbeat thudding]

10:23.120 --> 10:28.160
